<section class="fragment-review" data-artifact="review-command" data-dimension="reliability" data-rev="1">
<style>
.fr-rel-ok { background: var(--callout-ok-bg, #e8f5e9); border-left: 3px solid var(--callout-ok, #4caf50); padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.fr-rel-ok ul { padding-left: 1.4em; margin: 8px 0 0; }
</style>
<div class="fr-rel-ok">
  <strong>Reliability: Clean</strong> — no findings. Foundation slice has no critical paths to audit.
  <ul>
    <li>No auth, no payments, no data writes, no external service calls</li>
    <li>Scaffold components are render-only (no async error paths)</li>
    <li>No missing error boundaries for the current scope</li>
    <li>Cloudflare Workers platform provides built-in health monitoring</li>
    <li>Reliability patterns (circuit breakers, retry logic, timeouts) apply to later slices</li>
  </ul>
</div>
<script>
(function() {
  window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('sdlc:fragment-ready', {
    detail: { name: 'review-reliability', artifact: 'review-command', findings: 0, blockers: 0 }
  }));
})();
</script>
</section>
